content.winter_16.002: How do my lungs sound, doc? Sometimes they make a rattling sound when I exhale.
content.winter_15.000: I have a doctor's appointment tomorrow... Maybe the mermaid show will calm my nerves? But what if they think I'm ogling... *gulp*
content.winter_16.001: I'm seeing the doctor about my lungs... breathing in all that coal dust can't be good.
content.winter_16.000: I have a doctor's appointment today, so if you need to buy anything you'd better hurry.
